                <b class="h2">KONOMI</b>
                <b class="h1">Borrow and Lend</b>
              </div>
              <div class="h5">
                  A decentralised money market protocol for users to borrow and lend assets. The protocol is pool-based and it would support assets on parachains when the network is live. Users could deposit assets to the lending pool and earn interest based on the demand side of the platform. Similarly, the protocol also supports over-collateralized debt positions for users that want to borrow assets. Price data will be ultimately acquired through using off-chain workers to ensure that the lending pool is always secure from liquidation risks.
              </div>
